  V. Sim2-mih8 si5 khi2 chiah thang tam7 ai3. 
  A. Tam7 ai3 kho2-i2, tam7 loan7-ai3 put-kho2-i2. 
  Chong2-si7 lan2 tioh8 e7 ki3-tit, loan5-ai3 si7 hu-hu7-kan sin5-seng3 e5 thiaN3 cheng5. M7-si7 hu-hu7 e5 lam5-lu2 iN7-seng3 choe3-hoe2 tam7 loan5-ai3 si7 choe7-ok. Koh tioh8 e7 ki3-tit m7-si7 chheng-lian5 lam5-lu2 chit8-ban7-lang5, chit8-ban7-lang5 long2 tek-khak tioh8 keng-koe3 se3-kan sou2 kong2 ho7 choe3 loan5-ai3 e5 kau-poe5 chiah si7 lang5, chiah u7 ho2 e5 kiat-hun, na7 kiat-hun cheng5 bo5 seng tam7 loan5-ai3 chiu7 be7 choe3-chiaN5 ho2 e5 kiat-hun, che ia7 si7 chho3-gou7. 
  Lan2 thak8 Ku7-iok I2-sat kap Li7-pek-ka boe7 ke3, boe7 chhoa7 e5 i2-cheng5 long2 m7 saN-bat. Chong2-si7 in u7 choe3 ho2 e5 hu-hu7 seng-oah8. Hek8-chia2 lan2 e5 lo2-poe3 e5 sian-siN ia7 u7 che7-che7 chit khoan2 e5 keng-giam7. Sou2-i2 lan2 m7-bian2 be5-sin3 na7 bo5 seng loan5-ai3 (Chit ku3 ki5-sit8 be7 kong2-tit, thang kong2 tam7-ai3, a2-si7 ai3 e5 kau-poe5) , chiu7 be7-tit ke3 chhoa7. Na7-si7 hian7-tai7 che7-che7 chheng-lian5 chin be5-sin3 chit e5 su7. Koh sui-jian5 kiat-hun cheng5 toa7 kong2 loan5-ai3 e5 lang5, kau3 si5 ka-teng5 phoa3-lih8 e5 lang5 ia7 be7 chio2. 
