  (2) Thang ban2-kiu3 toe5-hoe3, liu5-loh8 hong3-tong7 e5 sim-keng2. 
  (3) Thang chhit-khi3 choat8-bang7, pi-chham2, iu-siong e5 bak8-sai2. 
  (4) Thang chio3-kng kio3-chheN2 ou-am3 be5-lou7 e5 sim-leng5. 
  (5) Thang hou7 thai5-lang5 pang3-hoe2 e5 hiong-hoan7 kui-cheng3. 
  Sio-lo7 e5 thiaN3-cheng5 chhin-chhiuN7 lun7-kut8-iu5 tih ti7 beh hoe2-sio-sim e5 ki-khi3, thang m7-bian2 hoat-hoe2. Chhin-chhiuN7 liat8-jit8 e7-tit siau-soaN3 kiat-oan3 chan5-jim2 e5 sim-tng5. Ka-teng5 hu-hu7 sio-lo7 e5 thiaN3. Pe7 kiaN2, bo2 kiaN2 sio-lo7 e5 thiaN3. HiaN-ti7 chi2-moai7 sio-lo7 e5 thiaN3 chin-chiaN3 po2-kui3 ah! 
  4. Tui3 sio-chim lai5 piau2-si7 ai3-cheng5. 
  Sio-chim, tek8-piat8 hu-hu7 e5 saN-chim si7 chit8-hang7 thiaN3 e5 piau2-hian7. Ti7 Seng3-keng u7 ka3-si7 lan2 cheng2-cheng2 e5 saN-chim. 
  (1) A-hiaN Iok-sek kap sio2-ti7 saN-chim (Chhong3 45:5). 
  (2) Ta-ke Na2-o-bi2 kap sim-pu7 Lou7-tek saN-chim (Lou7-tek 1:9). 
  (3) Sian-siN Po2-lo5 kap I2-hut-sou2 e5 hoe7-iu2 saN-chim 
  (4) Tai7-pit8 kap peng5-iu2 Iok-na2-tan saN-chim(Bo2 siong7 20:41). 
  (5) Lau7-pe7 Tai7-pit8 chim kiaN2 Ap-sa-liong5 (Bo2 ha7 14:63). 
  (6) Choe7-jin5 chim Chu2 Ia5-sou, lau5 bak8-sai2 hoan2-hoe2 (Lou7-ka 7:38). 
  (7) Kan-hiam2 e5 saN-chim. Iok-ap chim A-ma2-sat, ti7 A-ma2-sat bo5 the5-hong5 e5 si5 eng7 to tuh8 si2 i(Bo2 ha7 20:4). Iu5-tai7 eng7 chim-chhui3 be7 Ia5-sou (Thai3 26:48-49. Kho2 14:45-46. Lou7-ka 22:47-48). 
  (8) “Lin2 tioh8 eng7 seng3 e5 saN-chim lai5 saN chheng2-an.”(I Lim5 16:20). 
  Lam5-lu2 e5 saN-chim: 
  1. Na7 u7 chit8 e5 lam5-seng3 e7-hiau2 siuN7 ai3 X chit8 e5 lu2-seng3, an2-ni si7 hian2-beng5 hit e5 lam5-seng3 i2-keng si7 seng5-sek8 piN3 toa7-lang5 lah. Na7 u7 chit8 e5 lu2-seng3 chu7-hoat-tek XXX lai5 chim, hit e5 lu2-seng3 i2-keng lau7 lah. (Chim-kiaN2, chim-sun). 
  2. Hu-hu7 e5 saN-chim, bok8-hui si7 beh piau2-si7 thiaN3-cheng5, ke-thiN thiaN3-cheng5. Na7-si7 an2-ni ti7 su-ha7 nng7 lang5 ka-ti7 tiam3 e5 si5 lai5 choe3, pi2-kau3 khah hap8-li2, bo5 su-iau3 tng cheng5-lai5 kong-jian5 lai5 piau2-ian2. Lang5 khoaN3 liau2 m7-na7 bo5 sim-sek, u7-si5 soa3 e7 hou7 lang5 gin7-bak8. 
  3. Hu-hu7 saN-chhim, beh chhut-khi3 saN-chim, m7-tat8 tioh8 chhut-goa7 to3-lai5 e5 saN-chim iau2 khah tiN. Li2 na7 ai3 tiong7-hu siong5-siong5 khoaN3 li2 si7 pi2 pat8 e5 lu2-seng3 keng3 kho2-ai3 chiah e7. Lu2-seng3 chin e5 kho2-ai3, m7-si7 tui3 khiok-soaN3 e5 sui2, phang-chui2 e5 phang, hoe-hun2 e5 peh8. Khiok chiah e5 ko2-chin kui2-hun e7 pang-chan7 hou7 tiong7-hu ai3 chhin-kin7--li2. Chong2-si7 lam5-seng3 sim-te2 sou2 hoaN-hi2, sou2-ai3 e5 si7 lu2-seng3 un-cheng5 e5 chiau3-kou3, tiN-bit8 e5 an-ui3 kap kou2-le7. 
  Ti7 chia u7 chit8-hang7 chin ki5-koai3 e5 su7, chiu7-si7 seng3-chheh u7 ki3 cheng2-cheng2 e5 saN-chim na7 si7 m7-bat ki3 ang-bou2 e5 saN-chim. Sit8-chai7 chin chhu3-bi7, i3-gi7 bu5-kiong5. An2-ni tui3 i2-siong7 sou2 kong2 e5 lai5 khoaN3, saN-chim si7 jin5 cheng5 thiaN3-sim e5 chu7-jian5 liu5-lou7, sou2-i2 tek-khak tioh8 chhut tui3 chin-seng5 sun5-kiat, tek-khak m7-thang loan7-iong7, keng3-ka m7-thang ok-iong7 chiah ho2. Seng3-keng kong2 “Siong7-te3 m7-si7 hun-loan7 e5, si7 ho5-peng5 e5........ Hoan7-su7 tioh8 bun5-nga2 ia7 chiau3 kui-ki2 lai5 kiaN5.” Na7-si7 an2-ni kiam2-chhai2 u7 lang5 mng7 se-iuN5 chin seng7-heng5 saN-chim, an2-ni si7 ho2 a2 m7-ho2? Chiau3 khoaN3 che kap te7-li2, bun5-hoa3, jin5-cheng5, hong-siok8 u7 toa7 koan-he7. U7-si5 tang-iuN5 e5 le2-gi7 theh8 khi3 se-iuN5 be7 thong, chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni se-iuN5 e5 le2-gi7 theh8 lai5 lan2 tang-iuN5, u7 e5 ia7 be7 thong. Na7 be7 thong e5 su7, lang5 thi2-chhio3, kong-kek. Ho2, m7-ho2 si7 te7 ji7 bun7-te5. Sou2-i2 tui3 chit chan5 su7 tak8 lang5 thang ka-ti7 siuN7. 
  C. ThiaN3 e5 kek8-ti3 （愛e5極致）chiu7-si7 bu5-ngou2 hi-seng. 
  Lan2 na7 chu3-i3 thak8 Nga2-ko e5 seng3-keng e7 hoat-kian3 e7-bin7 sou2 ki3 e5 su7. 
  1. Nga2-ko 2:16. “Goa2 (chi2 sin-niu5) sou2 loan5-ai3 e5 siok8 goa2, goa2 ia7 siok8 i”(i chi2 tiong7-hu). 
  Ti7 chia sin-niu5 chiong pun2-sin choe3 pun2-ui7 lai5 kong2 i e5 tiong7-hu. Che si7 put-hian5 chu7-ki2 pun2-ui7 e5 lu2-seng3. 
  2. Nga2-ko 6:3 “Goa2 siok8 goa2 sou2 loan5-ai3 e5, goa2(chi2 sin-niu5) sou2 loan5-ai3 e5 ia7 siok8 goa2.” 
  Ti7 chia seng kong2 pun2-sin si7 siok8 i e5 tiong7-hu, jian5-au7 kong2 tiong7-hu ia7-si7 siok8 ti7 i. Ti7 chia u7 khah chin3-pou7, chiong tiong7-hu choe3 Chu2, pun2-sin choe3 pin lai5 kong2. 
  3. Nga2-ko 7:10. “Goa2(chi2 sin-niu5) siok8 goa2 sou2 loan5-ai3, I ia7 him-bou7 goa2.” 
  Ti7 chia sin-niu5 oan5-choan5 m7-kaN2 kong2 ka-ki7, oan5-choan5 eng7 tiong7-hu lai5 kong2. Kong2 i si7 siok8 ti7 tiong7-hu. M7-kaN2 kong2 tiong7-hu ia7-si7 siok8 ti7 i. Si7 kong2 tiong7-hu ia7 him-bou7 i, ji5-chhiaN2 I(chi2 tiong7-hu) si7 eng7 toa7-ho7-ji7 lai5 sia2. Chiu7-si7 tiong7-hu tiong-sim, i pun2-sin kam-goan7 oan5-choan5 but8-ngou2. Chiu7-si7 khoaN3 bo5 ka-ki7 lai5 ko-ku2 i e5 tiong7-hu. U7 iaN2, hu7-jin5-lang5 ti7 ka-teng5 chhin-chhiuN7 iam5 e5 po2-poe3. Iam5 e7 tiau-ho5 it-chhe3 hou7 long2-chong2 e5 mih8 hian2-chhut ho2 e5 bi7-sou3, koh m7-bian2 tu2-tioh8 hu2-pai7. Hu7-jin5-lang5 ia7-si7 an2-ni, hu7-jin5-lang5 ti7 ke-lai7 tiau-ho5, hou7 ka-teng5 tit-tioh8 iu-nga2, ho5-peng5, sio-lo7 e5 seng-oah8. Hou7 ka-teng5 u7 beng5-long2 e5 chhio3-siaN, hoan-lok8 e5 si-koa, hoat8-phoat e5 oah8-khi3. A-i5 ku7-kim7 sio-lo7 iu-nga2 e5 kau-poe5. Tiong7-hu tit-tioh8 pang-chan7 an-ui3, se3-kiaN2 tit-tioh8 poe5-iuN2 ka3-si7. Chit8 ke toan-toan-iN5. Hu7-jin5-lang5 lu2-seng3 e5 kong-lek8 toa7 ah! Chong2-si7 m7-thang chu7-ko sai7-phoat, ang2-lang2 koaiN7-phiah. Na2-chun2 iam5 chham ti7 thng e5 lai7-bin7 m7 soaN3, chit8-liap8 chit8-liap8 hou7 lang5 pou--tioh8, chhui3-khi2 un-un loh8-khi3, put-tek-i2 tioh8 ka7 i phui3-tiau7. Hu7-jin5-lang5 ia7-si7 an2-ni, ho2-kan-ho2, sui2 to sui2, na7-si7 ko3-seng3 thai3-kiong5, kap ke-lai7 ta-ke-koaN, toa7-peh sio2-chek, hiaN-so2 sio2-kou be7-ho5, chhiah-te7-te7, lian7 tiong7-hu to koan2 thau3-koe3. Ho2 to ho2, gau5 to gau5, kho2-sioh ui7 i chit8 lang5 thong-ke e5 chhui3-khi2 long2 khu5-khu5 loh8-khi3, u7-si5 kou-put-chiong e7 hou7 lang5 phui3 chhut--lai5. Iam5 e5 po2-poe3 chiu7-si7 bu5-ngou2, oan5-choan5 khoaN3 bo5 ka-ti7, goan7 iong5-hoa3 ti7 thng e5 lai7-bin7. Hou7 choan5-the2 tit-tioh8 bi2-bi7, i ka-ti7 oan5-choan5 hi-seng, che chiu7-si7 iam5 e5 po2-kui3, kap ui2-tai7 e5 sou2-chai7. Hu7-jin5-lang5 lu2-seng3 e5 ui2-tai7 po2-kui3 ia7-si7 chai7 ti7 chia. 
  Koh hu-hu7 e5 kiat-hap8 ia7-si7 chhin-chhiuN7 chui2 kap thou5. Chui2 hoan7 chui2, thou5 hoan7 thou5, chit8 hang7 ka7 i khng3 chit8-ui7 be7 choe3 sim2-mih8. Chong2-si7 thou5, chui2 ka7 i chhiau choe3-hoe2, au7-lai5 e7 choe3 chiaN5 khi3-khu7, oaN2, poaN5, ang3 tang7. Chiong hiah e5 jip8 io5 khi3 sio, ka7 i thng7-sek8 choe3 iu3-hui5. U7 e5 chin sui2 hou7 lang5 tui3-tiong7. Ti7 hia lan2 chi2-u7 khoaN3 tioh8 thou5 sio e5 hui5, long2 bo5 khoaN3 tioh8 chhiau thou5 e5 chui2. Chui2 chiu7-si7 lu2-seng3 hu7-jin5-lang5. I e7 pang-chan7 tiong7-hu seng5-ke ti3-hoe2, tiam2-peng chhut-chiong3, koaN ki ong5-hou7. Lang5 chi2-u7 khoaN3 i e5 tiong7-hu, ki5-sit8 chiu7-si7 u7 liong5-chhe ti7 au7-bin7. Io5 io-na5 e5 chhiu2, e7 io5-tang7 se3-kai3. Chiu7-si7 i sou2 io5 e5 kiaN2 chiong-lai5 khia7 ti7 thek-tha3 sam-kun, giu5-ni2 se3-kai3, ti7 koan5 e5 te7-ui7 hou7 lang5 o-lo2, na7-si7 i choe3 hian5-bo2 bih ti7 au7-bin7. Hoe2-chhia chin gau5 chau2, chun2-si5 lai5 un7-su hoe3, kheh hou7 lang5 toa7 o-lo2 li7-pian7. Ki5-sit8 na7 bo5 hiah e5 tiam7-tiam7 hou7 lang5 tai5 ti7 thou5-kha-te2, siu7 tam5 siu7 sip, jim2 hou7 peh8-hia7 chhia e5 kan-khou2, kau3-boe2 noa7-tiau7 ti7 thou5-lai7, eng2 bo5 khoaN3 tioh8 thian-jit8 e5 chim2-bok8-a2, chiu7 chhia chit8 pou7 to be7 chau2. Hiah e5 chim2-bok8-a2 chiu7-si7 lu2-seng3, hu7-jin5-lang5. Ah! Lu2-seng3, hu7-jin5-lang5 ah, lin2 sit8-chai7 chin hi-seng, lin2 tui3 ka-teng5, sia7-hoe7, kok-ka, se3-kai3 e5 kong3-hian3 sit8-chai7 ui2-tai7 ah! 
  Lan2 m7-thang siuN7 lu2-seng3 si7 chin loan2-jiok8, u7 iaN2, i chin nng2-chiaN2. Chong2-si7 koh chit8-bin7 i si7 chin kiong5. I pi2 lam5-seng3 peng5-kin khah nai7-mia7, khah gau5 jim2 thiaN3, jim2 koaN5, khah gau5 jim2 khou2. Sui-si7 eng-hiong5 ia7 lan5-koe3 bi2-jin5-koan. Ui7 chit8 e5 lu2-seng3 kok-ui7 hiat-kak8, chit8 kok e5 heng-soe, siaN5-ti5 e5 siu2, sit siong5-siong5 hou7 chit8 e5 lu2-seng3 cho2-iu7. Lu2-seng3 e5 ki-ti3, mou7-hiam2 sit8-chai7 thang kiaN, li2 khoaN3 se3-kai3 e5 kan2-tiap8(se3-choh) thoan5 lu2-seng3 e5 oah8-tang7. U7 iaN2, lu2-seng3 si7 chin ui2-tai7, chong2-si7 it-chhe3 e5 ui2-tai7 choe3-au7 iu5-goan5 si7 chai7 ti7 lu2-seng3 e5 bu5-ngou2 hi-seng e5 seng-oah8. An2-ni choe3 tiong7-hu e5 lam5-seng3 li2 beh eng7 chaiN2-iuN7 lai5 khoan2-thai7 li2 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5. I2-hut-sou2 5:25. “Choe3 tiong7-hu e5, lin2 tioh8 thiaN3 hu7-jin5-lang5, chhin-chhiuN7 Ki-tok thiaN3 kau3-hoe7, ia7 thoe3 i hian3 ka-ki7.” Tioh8 hian3-chhut li2 ka-ki7, chhin-chhiuN7 Ki-tok thiaN3 kau3-hoe7, ui7-tioh8 beh kiu3-siok8 kau3-hoe7 chiu7 kam-goan7 jim2-khou2 kau3 si2. Lam5-seng3 li2 iau-kiu5 lu2-seng3 ui7-tioh8 li2, ui7-tioh8 li2 chit8-ke lai5 hi-seng, lai5 si2, Li2 bat siuN7 li2 ia7 tioh8 ui7 lu2-seng3 lai5 hi-seng lai5 si2 a2-bo5? Eng3-kai u7, an2-ni chiah e7 peng5-heng5 peN5-pang7. Lam5-seng3 chiam3-iaN5, u7 chiN5 thang lim-chiu2, chiah8-hun hong-so, bo5 chiN5 thang thiah-ioh8 hou7 hu7-jin5-lang5 chiah8--e5 chin che7. Hu7-jin5-lang5 tai3 hu7-jin5-lang5-peN7 kong2 bo5 chiN5 thang ka7 i i, na7-si7 u7 chiN5 thang khi3 hoa-ke liu2-hang7 be2 chhio3 e5 be7 chio2. Cha-pou-lang5 ah! Bong-bong li2 e5 liong5-sim, ti7 chit-khoan2 e5 seng-oah8 beh ng3-bang7 kian3-chiaN5 tiN-bit8 bi2-moa2 e5 ka-teng5 choat8-tui3 bo5 ng3-bang7. 
  Koh kong2 chit8 pai2, bi2-moa2 tiN-bit8 e5 ka-teng5 m7-si7 chu7-jian5 u7--e5, si7 nng7-lang5 kiong7-tong5 kian3-cho7 e5. Chit8 e5 beh khiN5-ke, chit8 e5 m7, chu-chu siuN7 beh phoa3 ke, an2-ni bo5 hoat-tou7. Cha-pou than3, tioh8 ai3 cha-bou2 hoaN7, chit8 e5 chai, chit8 e5 ak-chui2, an2-ni chiah e7 chiah8 tioh8 heng7-hok ai3-cheng5 e5 koe2-chi2. Tioh8 e7 ki3-tit hou7--lang5 pi2 theh8--lang5 khah u7 hok-khi3. ThiaN3-cheng5 ia7-si7 an2-ni. Lan2 u7 liong7 thang thiaN3--lang5, pi2 tiaN7 siuN7 beh tit lang5 thiaN3 e5 khah ho2. Tak8-lang5 to chu7-jian5 u7 thiaN3--lang5 e5 sim, siang7-si5 tak8 lang5 to ng3-bang7 lang5 thiaN3. Lang5 ti7 se3-kan sim-lai7 na7 bo5 thiaN3 poaN3 lang5, siang7-si5 ia7 kam2-kak bo5 poaN3-lang5 thiaN3 i, an2-ni hit e5 lang5 e7 kam2-kak chin pi-chham2, kou-tok8, bo5 liau5, u7 si5 e7 khi2-siau2, hek8-chia2 e7 kau3 chu7-sat. Tui3 lang5 si-ai3, na7 u7 lang5 seng5-siu7, kam2-kak chin hoaN-hi2. Na7 u7 chit8 e5 lang5 chiong i e5 ai3-cheng5 beh hou7 lang5, ia7 bo5 lang5 ai3 ka7 i seng5-siu7, i e7 chin loe2-chi3, u7 si5 e7 chu7-pou7 chu7-khi3, u7 si5 e7 seN khi2 sat-jin5, chu7-sat e5 kheng-ki2 bong5-tong7. Hit e5 lang5 na7 chiong 5 hun thiaN3 beh hou7 i e5 tui3-siong7, i e5 tui3-siong7 m7-tihN8. An2-ni e7 hoan2-to3-tng2 oan3 i 5 hun, m7-si7, u7 si5 soa3 piN3 oan3 i 8 hun. Na7 chiong 10 hun thiaN3 beh hou7 i e5 tui3-siong7. I e5 tui3-siong7 khi2-thau5 na2-chun2 boeh, au7-lai5 ui7 ...... soa3 hoan2 khi3-khiok, soa3 biau2-si7, ku7-choat8 hit e5 thiaN3. Hit-si5 e5 hoan2-eng3 m7-si7 sio2-khoa2. U7-si5 e7 eng7 si2 phoe3 ...... i3, lai5 pai5-siat ai3 siu7 ku7-choat8 e5 hin7. Na7 lu2--e5 bo5 hoat-tit lam5--e5 ta-oa5, khah siong5 e7 khi2-siau2, chu7-sat, a2-si7 iau3-kiu5 choe3-hoe2 si2. Na7 lam5--e5 e7 jia2 chhut hui2-iong5,(eng7 ioh8-chui2 phoah lu2 e5 bin7 hou7 i noa7, a2-si7 hou7 i chhiN-mi5) a2-si7 sat-jin5 e5 su7-kiaN7. U7 si5 m7-na7 thai5 tui3-siong7 e5 lu2-seng3, lian5 chou2-tong3 e5 pe7-bo2 to e7 chiah8-khui. Hit-si5 e5 sim-li2 pi2 ia2-gu5, pi2 khip-hiat-kui2 koh khah li7-hai7. Sou2-i2 lam5-lu2 iN7-seng3-kan choat8-tui3 m7-thang sui5-pian7 iok-sok ai3-cheng5, jian5-au7 sui5-pian7 koh saN poe7, u7-si5 e7 jia2-chhut liau7 be7 tioh8 e5 chai-ho7. 
  Ai3-cheng5 m7-si7 eng7 chiN5 e7-tit boe2--lai5 e5, ia7 m7-si7 e7-tit hou7 li2 eng7 tiN-gian5 bit8-gu2 phian3--lai5, koai2--lai5 e5. Ai3-cheng5 si7 ai3 tui3 seng5-sim seng5-i3, lau5-koaN7, piaN3-mia7 eng7 sim keh-kau3, liu5-sim hoe7-sin5 lai5 choe3, it-seng e5 kiat-chok. Si7 sim-leng5-tek ge7-sut8 e5 piau2-hian7. Hu-hu7 na2-lau7 si7 na2-sui2, lau7-bou2 e5 bin7 na2-jiau5 khiok-soaN3 kng-am3 na2 hun-beng5, che chiah si7 bi2-sut8 e5 piau2-hian7. M7-si7 lau7 tioh8 bo5 ho2 siaN-khui3, ku7-khim5 chai-seng3 na2 ti-im chiah e7 na2 chhut ho5-hai5 e5 siaN. 
